#this is the advanced tab under preferences


#Speech Command Integration (Future Feature):


    #Voice Command Toggle: Toggle to enable/disable speech commands.
    #Command Customization: Settings to define custom commands (e.g., “Next profile”, “Replay last TTS”).

#Input Auto-Completion: Allows users to complete input by selecting from a list of suggested completions.
    #Input Auto-Suggestion Delay: Sets a delay before displaying auto-suggestions.
    #Input Auto-Suggestion Mode: Options for how auto-suggestions should be displayed (e.g., in a dropdown menu, inline).
    #Input Auto-Suggestion Hotkeys: Custom hotkeys for triggering auto-suggestions.
    #Input Auto-Suggestion Animation: A visual effect when auto-suggestions are displayed.




